      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HE'S A MENACE (2) turned in a plain effort last time when eighth at this track over 272m behind Feed The Meter (17.11) in a Maiden. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Looks the one to beat on his best form. MY BLUE BATTLER (7) showed good early burn but run over late to finish 6th at this track in Maiden company. The form from her last run stacks up well. Expected to run well. KILCOY PEARL (4) shows ability but remains a maiden after 14 starts. Was fifth (22.83) at Gosford latest and although yet to win tends to go well here. Can measure up this time. SHE'S CASHED UP (1) is worth a look despite no experience at this circuit.",
